	   <tr><td colspan=2>Yes this is the normal mele dmg for the 52nd fire pet. It is a wiz pet and nukes a lot more than the 49th pet. It's ok for groups but don't think about using it to solo anything close to our lvl. It casts a varity of different nukes including an aoe. Also puts a dmg shield on any other pet in the group.<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
