	   <tr><td colspan=2>I am a newbie (lvl 3) mage seeking advice on allocating practice points.  So far I have put most into magic skills and still have 3 points I haven't used.  Should I put all into magic skills, use some to develop a trade skill, is there an advantage to saving practices and using them at higher levels?  I am in the dark on this.  Also, as a mage is it better to specialize in piercing, 1HB, or 2HB for a melee weapon.<br><br><br>Tarvek, Luclin Server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
