	   <tr><td colspan=2>There really aren't many magician only quests. Sort of the downs about being a magician. Although at your level you can start collecting items to do the focus items quests at the temple of solusek ro. You can find information on this very sight. It says you have to be level 30 to start, but thats not true. One of my magicians had all of high focus items except the fire one at level 16. Oh, and the focus items work on pets that are below level 34, its not true that they only work on level 34+ pets.<br><br>Just ask higher level characters to help you out on getting the items you need almost all of them are inexpensive and high level players will simply give you if you go to the correct zones and ask for them. The only things that are costly are the gems that you have to buy for every focus item. Its something like 250pp for all of the gems combined, maybe a bit more. If you fight wisps that is easy money though.<br><br>Former Everquest Addict.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
