	   <tr><td colspan=2>I have a Level 3 Mage (High Elf) and need some info... I keep reading stuff about people training and specializing, etc... when people say training do they mean what shows up as "practice" on the game?  And what is with this specializing business, can someone elaborate on that a little?<br><br>Thanks for any help...<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
